{"page_url": "https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gears-of-war-designer-pleads-to-keep-chris-pratt-away-from-the-netflix-movie/1100-6509119/", "page_title_en": "Gears Of War Designer Pleads To Keep Chris Pratt Away From The Netflix Movie", "page_title_ko": "", "page_title_cn": "", "page_description_en": "\"Keep Chris Pratt away from the Gears franchise, please, FFS.\"", "page_description_ko": "", "page_description_cn": "", "page_author": "Eddie Makuch", "page_date": "2022-11-14T09:05:07-0800", "page_text_html": "\n                <p>Netflix is making a <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gears-of-war-movie-and-animated-series-coming-to-netflix/1100-6508970/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6508970\">Gears of War movie</a>, and if the game's original designer had any say in the casting--which he does not--he would not choose Chris Pratt. Cliff Bleszinski, who designed the Gears of War series at Epic Games before <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/cliff-bleszinski-out-at-epic-games/1100-6397630/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6397630\">departing the studio in 2012</a>, lobbied to \"keep Pratt away\" from the series.</p><p>In a tweet, Bleszinski reacted to the Gears of War x Netflix news, saying, \"Oh and keep Chris Pratt away from the Gears franchise, please, FFS.\" He didn't offer up any rationale as to why he wouldn't want Pratt to appear in the Gears of War movie or any other extension of the universe.</p><p>Bleszinski did, however, agree with the joke that <a href=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1589742290888585216\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">it would be funny for Pratt to play all members of the Carmine family.</a> This being the internet, someone very quickly created mock-up images of Pratt as Gears of War characters--check out the images below.</p><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1589731094701957120\" data-has-image=\"false\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 10px auto; display: flex; max-width: 550px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-0\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\" title=\"Twitter Tweet\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?creatorScreenName=GameSpot&amp;dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-0&amp;&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=true&amp;id=1589731094701957120&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fgears-of-war-designer-pleads-to-keep-chris-pratt-away-from-the-netflix-movie%2F1100-6509119%2F&amp;sessionId=8f22355abf9a44eb159e38720408c14d5911111b&amp;siteScreenName=GameSpot&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=a3525f077c700%3A1667415560940&amp;width=550px\" data-tweet-id=\"1589731094701957120\"></iframe></div><blockquote align=\"center\" class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-mce-disable-toolbar=\"true\" data-twitter-extracted-i1669110618057517436=\"true\"><p dir=\"ltr\">Oh and keep Chris Pratt away from the Gears franchise, please, FFS.</p>  \u2014 Cliff Bleszinski (@therealcliffyb) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1589731094701957120?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 7, 2022</a></blockquote>              <script type=\"text/javascript\" class=\"optanon-category-C0004\" async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" data-service-name=\"twitter\" id=\"twitter-embed-1938364181\" src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\"></script></div><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/TheIndigoGaming/status/1589852046605574144\" data-has-image=\"true\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 10px auto; display: flex; max-width: 550px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-1\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\" title=\"Twitter Tweet\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?creatorScreenName=GameSpot&amp;dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-1&amp;&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=true&amp;id=1589852046605574144&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fgears-of-war-designer-pleads-to-keep-chris-pratt-away-from-the-netflix-movie%2F1100-6509119%2F&amp;sessionId=8f22355abf9a44eb159e38720408c14d5911111b&amp;siteScreenName=GameSpot&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=a3525f077c700%3A1667415560940&amp;width=550px\" data-tweet-id=\"1589852046605574144\"></iframe></div><blockquote align=\"center\" class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-mce-disable-toolbar=\"true\" data-twitter-extracted-i1669110618057517436=\"true\"><p dir=\"ltr\">I'm sorry, Cliff. I had to. <a href=\"https://t.co/yG57fXbRD5\" rel=\"nofollow \">pic.twitter.com/yG57fXbRD5</a></p>  \u2014 Indigo Gaming (@TheIndigoGaming) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheIndigoGaming/status/1589852046605574144?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 8, 2022</a></blockquote>              <script type=\"text/javascript\" class=\"optanon-category-C0004\" async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" data-service-name=\"twitter\" id=\"twitter-embed-1482262416\" src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\"></script></div><p>As for who Bleszinski believes should be in the Gears of War film, he said Ryan Reynolds would \"make a perfect Baird.\" Bleszinski is <a href=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1590524648151580673\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">not involved in the Gears of War Netflix movie</a>, so he's only offering up his thoughts and opinions and doesn't hold any decision-making power.</p><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1589742836874088450\" data-has-image=\"true\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 10px auto; display: flex; max-width: 550px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-2\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\" title=\"Twitter Tweet\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?creatorScreenName=GameSpot&amp;dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-2&amp;&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=true&amp;id=1589742836874088450&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fgears-of-war-designer-pleads-to-keep-chris-pratt-away-from-the-netflix-movie%2F1100-6509119%2F&amp;sessionId=8f22355abf9a44eb159e38720408c14d5911111b&amp;siteScreenName=GameSpot&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=a3525f077c700%3A1667415560940&amp;width=550px\" data-tweet-id=\"1589742836874088450\"></iframe></div><blockquote align=\"center\" class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-mce-disable-toolbar=\"true\" data-twitter-extracted-i1669110618057517436=\"true\"><p dir=\"ltr\">I think <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VancityReynolds?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@VancityReynolds</a> would make a perfect Baird in the live action <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GearsofWar?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#GearsofWar</a> movie. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/netflix?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@netflix</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/78qMdt9kto\" rel=\"nofollow \">https://t.co/78qMdt9kto</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/IFKnskptku\" rel=\"nofollow \">pic.twitter.com/IFKnskptku</a></p>  \u2014 Cliff Bleszinski (@therealcliffyb) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1589742836874088450?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 7, 2022</a></blockquote>              <script type=\"text/javascript\" class=\"optanon-category-C0004\" async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" data-service-name=\"twitter\" id=\"twitter-embed-1113849445\" src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\"></script></div><p>Dave Bautista, who has petitioned to play Gears of War lead Marcus Fenix for years while the Gears of War film was in various stages of development, put out another video recently in which he lobbied to star in the Gears of War movie. \"I can't make this any easier,\" he said. For what it's worth, Bleszinski replied to the video and said <a href=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1590849559743279104\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bautista is his first choice to play Fenix.</a></p><p>Bleszinski also said he believes Karl Urban (The Boys, The Lord of the Rings) could be a prime candidate to play Fenix.</p><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/DaveBautista/status/1590837419791695872\" data-has-image=\"true\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 10px auto; display: flex; max-width: 550px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-3\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"position: static; visibility: visible; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\" title=\"Twitter Tweet\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?creatorScreenName=GameSpot&amp;dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-3&amp;&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=true&amp;id=1590837419791695872&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fgears-of-war-designer-pleads-to-keep-chris-pratt-away-from-the-netflix-movie%2F1100-6509119%2F&amp;sessionId=8f22355abf9a44eb159e38720408c14d5911111b&amp;siteScreenName=GameSpot&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=a3525f077c700%3A1667415560940&amp;width=550px\" data-tweet-id=\"1590837419791695872\"></iframe></div><blockquote align=\"center\" class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-mce-disable-toolbar=\"true\" data-twitter-extracted-i1669110618057517436=\"true\"><p dir=\"ltr\">I can\u2019t make this any easier. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GearsofWar?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gearsofwar</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/netflix?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@netflix</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/marcusfenix?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#marcusfenix</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GearsofWar?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#GearsofWar</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/SzDpiT2rNA\" rel=\"nofollow \">pic.twitter.com/SzDpiT2rNA</a></p>  \u2014 Dave Bautista (@DaveBautista) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DaveBautista/status/1590837419791695872?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 10, 2022</a></blockquote>              <script type=\"text/javascript\" class=\"optanon-category-C0004\" async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" data-service-name=\"twitter\" id=\"twitter-embed-942055378\" src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\"></script></div><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1589730269434908672\" data-has-image=\"false\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 10px auto; display: flex; max-width: 550px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-4\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; flex-grow: 1;\" title=\"Twitter Tweet\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?creatorScreenName=GameSpot&amp;dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-4&amp;&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=true&amp;id=1589730269434908672&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fgears-of-war-designer-pleads-to-keep-chris-pratt-away-from-the-netflix-movie%2F1100-6509119%2F&amp;sessionId=8f22355abf9a44eb159e38720408c14d5911111b&amp;siteScreenName=GameSpot&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=a3525f077c700%3A1667415560940&amp;width=550px\" data-tweet-id=\"1589730269434908672\"></iframe></div><blockquote align=\"center\" class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-mce-disable-toolbar=\"true\" data-twitter-extracted-i1669110618057517436=\"true\"><p dir=\"ltr\">I could also see Karl Urban as Marcus, folks.<br>Fuckin' diabolical.</p>  \u2014 Cliff Bleszinski (@therealcliffyb) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/therealcliffyb/status/1589730269434908672?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 7, 2022</a></blockquote>              <script type=\"text/javascript\" class=\"optanon-category-C0004\" async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" data-service-name=\"twitter\" id=\"twitter-embed-2022287397\" src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\"></script></div><p>In addition to the live-action Gears of War movie, <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gears-of-war-movie-and-animated-series-coming-to-netflix/1100-6508970/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6508970\">Netflix is producing a Gears of War anime</a>. As for the game series, 2019's Gears 5 is the latest entry in the series and no new games have been announced.</p><p>Developer The Coalition has <a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gears-studio-the-coalition-confirms-two-projects-in-development-will-use-unreal-engine-5/1100-6491245/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6491245\">multiple new games in development</a>, and while they remain a secret, it's a safe bet that at least one of them is a Gears of War title.</p>\n  \n                        \n    \n        <div class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-mpu_middle mapped-mpu_middle-dart js-seamless-middle-mpu float-right no-inner-space\" data-ad-type=\"mpu_middle\"><div class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-mpu_middle\"></div></div>\n        <div class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-mpu_bottom mapped-mpu_bottom-dart js-seamless-bottom-mpu float-right no-inner-space\" data-ad-type=\"mpu_bottom\"><div class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-mpu_bottom\"></div></div>\n  \n                        <div class=\"js-inline-widget\" id=\"inline-bottom\"></div>          ", "page_text_en": "Netflix is making a Gears of War movie, and if the game's original designer had any say in the casting--which he does not--he would not choose Chris Pratt. Cliff Bleszinski, who designed the Gears of War series at Epic Games before departing the studio in 2012, lobbied to \"keep Pratt away\" from the series.\n\nIn a tweet, Bleszinski reacted to the Gears of War x Netflix news, saying, \"Oh and keep Chris Pratt away from the Gears franchise, please, FFS.\" He didn't offer up any rationale as to why he wouldn't want Pratt to appear in the Gears of War movie or any other extension of the universe.\n\nBleszinski did, however, agree with the joke that it would be funny for Pratt to play all members of the Carmine family. This being the internet, someone very quickly created mock-up images of Pratt as Gears of War characters--check out the images below.\n\nOh and keep Chris Pratt away from the Gears franchise, please, FFS.\n\n\u2014 Cliff Bleszinski (@therealcliffyb) November 7, 2022\n\nI'm sorry, Cliff. I had to. pic.twitter.com/yG57fXbRD5\n\n\u2014 Indigo Gaming (@TheIndigoGaming) November 8, 2022\n\nAs for who Bleszinski believes should be in the Gears of War film, he said Ryan Reynolds would \"make a perfect Baird.\" Bleszinski is not involved in the Gears of War Netflix movie, so he's only offering up his thoughts and opinions and doesn't hold any decision-making power.\n\nI think @VancityReynolds would make a perfect Baird in the live action #GearsofWar movie. @netflix https://t.co/78qMdt9kto pic.twitter.com/IFKnskptku\n\n\u2014 Cliff Bleszinski (@therealcliffyb) November 7, 2022\n\nDave Bautista, who has petitioned to play Gears of War lead Marcus Fenix for years while the Gears of War film was in various stages of development, put out another video recently in which he lobbied to star in the Gears of War movie. \"I can't make this any easier,\" he said. For what it's worth, Bleszinski replied to the video and said Bautista is his first choice to play Fenix.\n\nBleszinski also said he believes Karl Urban (The Boys, The Lord of the Rings) could be a prime candidate to play Fenix.\n\nI can\u2019t make this any easier. @gearsofwar @netflix #marcusfenix #GearsofWar pic.twitter.com/SzDpiT2rNA\n\n\u2014 Dave Bautista (@DaveBautista) November 10, 2022\n\nI could also see Karl Urban as Marcus, folks.\nFuckin' diabolical.\n\n\u2014 Cliff Bleszinski (@therealcliffyb) November 7, 2022\n\nIn addition to the live-action Gears of War movie, Netflix is producing a Gears of War anime. As for the game series, 2019's Gears 5 is the latest entry in the series and no new games have been announced.\n\nDeveloper The Coalition has multiple new games in development, and while they remain a secret, it's a safe bet that at least one of them is a Gears of War title.", "page_text_ko": "", "page_text_cn": "", "page_tags": ["Gears 5", "Xbox One", "Xbox Series X", "PC"], "page_images": [], "page_videos": ""}